article.description: — David Jenkins Jr. had 26 points as UNLV edged past Air Force 69-64 on Monday night.
article.headline: Jenkins Jr. scores 26 to lift UNLV over Air Force 69-64
article.linkText: Jenkins Jr. scores 26 to lift UNLV over Air Force 69-64
article.story: LAS VEGAS -- — David Jenkins Jr. had 26 points as UNLV edged past Air Force 69-64 on Monday night. Jenkins Jr. hit 6 of 8 3-pointers. Bryce Hamilton had 14 points for UNLV (8-9, 5-5 Mountain West Conference). Cheikh Mbacke Diong added nine rebounds and four blocks. A.J. Walker had 20 points for the Falcons (4-14, 2-12), who have now lost seven straight games. Nikc Jackson added 18 points. The Runnin’ Rebels improve to 2-0 against the Falcons on the season. UNLV defeated Air Force 68-58 on Saturday. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
